cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SE, cs.PL 

The paper deals with the problem of repairing blockchains, which involves aspects of cryptography, distributed computing, and software engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
